### Design Decisions Reached
- Company: klökwork Inc / klökwork AI
- Product: kre8 by klökwork AI
- GitHub org: klokworkai, mono-repo: klokworkai/kre8
- Full component renaming locked (kre8_think→kre8, kre8_agent→konnekt, etc.)
- Component phasing: Phase 1 Pilot, Phase 2.1, Phase 2.2, Phase 3
- DesignPlan renamed to Kanvas (schema level only)
- StructuredIntent (SI) name retained
- kure absorbs kcheck — validate + self-correct is sub-module of koder
- skout = semantic search engine (katalog + kpedia)
- kpedia: three collections — pillars, forums, utd_docs
- koder owns Context7 integration (write-through cache → kpedia/utd_docs)
- Cache strategy: cache-first, TTL-based refresh via kron (Phase 2.2)
- TF registry governance: kodex allowlist + kontext private registry URL
- CLAUDE.md + ABOUTME.md live at workspace root (not in repo)
- claude.log lives in docs/ inside the repo
